Scope of this open-source release (open-core)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This public repository contains the *recevability framework* for LLM-assisted
financial analysis: the Recommendation Record schema, the evaluation gates
(G-1..G-6), deterministic reference computation, synthetic fixtures, and mock
connectors. See OPEN-CORE.md for the precise public/enterprise boundary.

It does NOT contain, and never will:
  - real market or fundamentals data,
  - production data connectors (EDGAR, EODHD, FMP, Tiingo, Sharadar, ...),
  - proprietary scoring, MARBO FINANCE integrations, or operational
    compliance workflows.

